Grounded pops out of the ground.  The blind bot listens for 
movement hearing Lokk moving.  Knowing it is Lokk by a detailed 
power scan, Grounded runs to him.  "Lokk, it is over again, but 
they will come again and again.  I think we must attack them soon, 
very soon.

Seekker jumps out of the pod.  "Thank you, thank you very much.  
I, did. try my hardest in this fight, adn thanks to my valiat, brave 
efforts, we were able to win this fight.  " Seekker said in the 
cockiest movie tone ever.
